Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NYou're just like a little bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with a hundred\Nthousand more weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,our chore boy can still\Nbring him to his knees...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,... because he\Ndoes not know fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG, LUFFY yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When he's fighting...\Nhe's not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even death!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just instinct,\Nor all a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll know soon, if he lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NWhat plan? Killing himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NToday is your funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh?! What? my Battle Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just punched it in\Nthe head five times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks tired,\Nmaybe it needs a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Chore Boy's pretty good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be able to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He just shattered the\NMighty Battle Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle he's still alive\Nafter that many explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he can hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "The Conclusion\Nof the Deadly Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A Spear of Blind Determination!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou ready for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBecause that was all I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that your little toy's\Nbroken, you're nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG grunts]\NOh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just a bomb on a\Nstick and let's face it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that's pretty lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NYou think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSure do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG] Heh. Fine, so what if\Nit is just a bomb on a stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in sad shape, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be more than\Nenough to blow you to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya know, it sounds to me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,like this is some sort of\Npathetic attempt at a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your defeat is imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, when you defied me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You signed your\Nown death warrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, KRIEG grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHey! Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gibbers]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bounce outta that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How many weapons\Ndoes that guy have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that kid doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like there's\Narms everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG laugning]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NWeakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly did you\Nexpect to happen, Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing Wootz\NSteel Body Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This stuff is practically\Nindestructible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY inhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, KRIEG grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NDon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHow dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.\NYou'll never defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This armor could take a million\Nmore of your monkey punches
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and it wouldn't have\Nso much as a dent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll just see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHe's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NI'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NYou don't stand a chance, Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Real power comes\Nfrom deadly weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the source\Nof true strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See, only the strong\Nare meant to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? That's what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish pride will\Nonly get you so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,... Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing] That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that big talk,\Nthat's all you've got? Ha, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it,\Nmy armor's cracking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHeh! Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done for, chore boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHe's not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just instinct,\Nor all a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll know soon, if he lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES shout]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS cheer]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COOK A] All right!\N--[COOK L] Way to go chore boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[KREIG]\NThis isn't over yet, Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoah, he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[KREIG laughing]\NYou can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a steel net!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over! That's the ocean\Ndown there below us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I'll be getting\Nthe last laugh after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES cheering]\N--[PIRATE E] Take him down Don!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE F]\NMake that little brat pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE G]\NYeah, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I got that jerk\Nright where I want him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHe hasn't even flinched.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he stay so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Time for me\Nto end this, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,... Giant Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,... Giant Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[chcukles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COOKS cheer]\N--[PIRATE CC] No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Krieg was defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J]\NHow could this have happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK L]\NYou're awesome, Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK M]\NYeah, you kicked his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,--[CARNE laughs]\N--He won! He really won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta be dreamin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Don Krieg\Nwe're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY] I know! Who'd a thought\Nthat kid had it in 'im?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] What is it?\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Rise and shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Krieg was beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Betcha you never thought\Nyou'd see the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done daydreaming, yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, save that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHe can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Those with the\Npower of the Devil Fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,are hated by the sea, so they\Nlose their ability to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you sayin'?\NHe'll just sink?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've told\Nme that sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you worthless old geezer!\NWhat if it's already too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHeh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHey! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NYou said you wouldn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly believe that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] You'll have to\Ndo better than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,... if you want to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, I don't think it's\Ntime for me to die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThese guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] How this fight would\Nend was clear from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why choose death?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! Give up\Nyour ambition and live!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThey're all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I don't know...\Nbut, I will not run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I retreat a single step,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be shattering\Nthe promises I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I would lose my honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, without that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be nothing\Nleft for me, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Even with a hundred\Nthousand more weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,our chore boy can still\Nbring him to his knees,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because he does not know fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Krieg may have more\Npirates at his command,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,he may have terrible weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that cause mass destruction\Nto everything in his path,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but he will never\Nhave that kid's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThe All Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Hey, Chore Boy,\Ndon't you die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES whimper]\N--[PIRATE G] Don! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE H]\NPlease, tell us it's an act!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NDon Krieg has been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the mighty rule\N of the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY] Yeah? Well, now\Nhe's down for the count!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a look at him\Nand see for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE] That fancy armor\Nof his got all busted up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and he was out as soon\Nas he hit the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Do you think\Nwe're lying to ya'?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the only man\NI ever really admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish, now he's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NHey! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you move now,\Nthe poison'll set in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE] Be still!\NIt's for your own good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NChore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chore Boy, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have a lot of\Nthings to do with your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NNo! I'm the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I win! I'm the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No one defeats me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Just stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop him! He's not\Neven conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATE J] Please Don, stop!\N--[PIRATES yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to win! I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES shout]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,--[KRIEG yells]\N--[PIRATES scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG howling]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight until\Nvictory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NDon Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NCommander?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] Let's leave now, while we\Nstill have a shred of dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] Sure, now leave\Nand don't ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHey, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't owe me any favors,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but when the kid wakes up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] Tell him I said I'll\Nsee him on the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NBut, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I wanna go\Nwith the time I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only\Nthing I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that\Nkeeps me going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. It would seem that\NDon Krieg's obsession
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Grand Line, has\Nbecome mine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But, It's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,With this poison in my veins,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I may only have a\Nfew hours to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I feel free somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,like now I can live those last\Nfew moments on my own terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY,CARNE panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] To hell with\Nloyalty to Don Krieg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My devotion to him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,was just an escape from\Nforging my own destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you heart is set,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and you pursue all your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with every last fiber\Nof what you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you will never again feel lost,\Nor hopeless, or afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned all that fro\N a brave chore boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him the boat we use\Nto go grocery shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Are you\Nstupid or somethin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to give\Na perfectly good boat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to a bunch of pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's gonna happen to all\Nour grocery shopping, Jackass?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Patty's right. Let 'em swim\Nwherever they're goin' to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get that grocery boat, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE sob]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop shouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE]\NOkay, okay, we'll go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES yelling, grumbling]\N--[PIRATE J] It's gonna sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NWhy did I hesitate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I so worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think about it,\NI can't help but feel stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY snoring]\N--[GHIN, SANJI] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NWell then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We gratefully accept this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right to assume there's\Nno need to return it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NIt's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even to return this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NHe's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't you ever forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the restaurant\Nwhere the cooks fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baratie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN] Heh. The cooks\Nthere sure mean business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.89,0:22:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure were nice guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they would\Nlet me join them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,, I hope I see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Free. I just wanna be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellemere...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.37,0:23:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.51,0:24:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.64,0:24:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.99,0:24:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI guess I can leave now,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.28,0:24:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,since me and pops\Nmade that deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.99,0:24:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NThat's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSo, you wanna--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] I'm not gonna run\Naway to become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.33,0:24:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWell, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.66,0:24:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHaven't you given up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I am hoping to go\Nto the Grand Line someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.42,0:24:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThen, let's go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.80,0:24:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NIt's not the right time, yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.88,0:24:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.34,0:24:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.38,0:24:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seafaring Cook\NSets off With Luffy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.93,0:24:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

